  "lyrics": "You, oh you, yeah you And baby, just right now You got me walkin', baby got me walkin' Ooh, you got me walkin', baby got me walkin' Oh no I'm on a tightrope, wow, I can't know left, right Which way you want me to go Yeah, which way you want me, what Cause you got me walkin' in a single by night Can't walk it to the left, can't walk it to the right I don't even know where's the good spot I'm woo, woo, walkin' on a tightrope Woo, yeah, I'm walkin' on a tightrope Oh, you know what you do, yeah You know how you make me go left, make me go right I don't know which way we have to Fight again and you'll run away Lighting your light in your mind Fading light in your mind I'm on a tightrope, baby, tightrope, baby You're making me go crazy Woo, got me walkin' on a tightrope Woo, you got me walkin' on a tightrope, baby Woo, all right, which way we go Left, right, none of that's gonna be it I'm on a tightrope You got me, woo, woo, all night long, yeah You got me fucked up, yeah And I had a good night",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 8.260000228881836,
      "text": "You, oh you, yeah you",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 13.15999984741211,
      "text": "And baby, just right now",
      "start": 8.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 16.579999923706055,
      "text": "You got me walkin', baby got me walkin'",
      "start": 13.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 23.399999618530273,
      "text": "Ooh, you got me walkin', baby got me walkin'",
      "start": 17.700000762939453
    },
    {
      "end": 25.959999084472656,
      "text": "Oh no",
      "start": 23.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 30.18000030517578,
      "text": "I'm on a tightrope, wow, I can't know left, right",
      "start": 26.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 33.900001525878906,
      "text": "Which way you want me to go",
      "start": 30.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 39.040000915527344,
      "text": "Yeah, which way you want me, what",
      "start": 34.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 45.68000030517578,
      "text": "Cause you got me walkin' in a single by night",
      "start": 39.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 49.2599983215332,
      "text": "Can't walk it to the left, can't walk it to the right",
      "start": 45.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 52.08000183105469,
      "text": "I don't even know where's the good spot",
      "start": 49.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 59.439998626708984,
      "text": "I'm woo, woo, walkin' on a tightrope",
      "start": 52.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 66.30000305175781,
      "text": "Woo, yeah, I'm walkin' on a tightrope",
      "start": 59.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 73.08000183105469,
      "text": "Oh, you know what you do, yeah",
      "start": 67.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 82.33999633789062,
      "text": "You know how you make me go left, make me go right",
      "start": 75.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 86.45999908447266,
      "text": "I don't know which way we have to",
      "start": 82.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 90.68000030517578,
      "text": "Fight again and you'll run away",
      "start": 87.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 93.80000305175781,
      "text": "Lighting your light in your mind",
      "start": 90.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 98.22000122070312,
      "text": "Fading light in your mind",
      "start": 93.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 102.13999938964844,
      "text": "I'm on a tightrope, baby, tightrope, baby",
      "start": 98.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 105.95999908447266,
      "text": "You're making me go crazy",
      "start": 102.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 111.87999725341797,
      "text": "Woo, got me walkin' on a tightrope",
      "start": 107.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 119.0999984741211,
      "text": "Woo, you got me walkin' on a tightrope, baby",
      "start": 113.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 125.26000213623047,
      "text": "Woo, all right, which way we go",
      "start": 121.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 129.1199951171875,
      "text": "Left, right, none of that's gonna be it",
      "start": 125.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 132.25999450683594,
      "text": "I'm on a tightrope",
      "start": 129.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 139.25999450683594,
      "text": "You got me, woo, woo, all night long, yeah",
      "start": 133.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 143.66000366210938,
      "text": "You got me fucked up, yeah",
      "start": 140.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 145.32000732421875,
      "text": "And I had a good night",
